univention-management-console (6.0.24-6) unstable; urgency=low

  * don't let UMC module processes die by timeout if the time delta seems to be
    unnatural (e.g. due to huge jumps in wall-clock time through NTP updates)
    (Bug #34105)
  * fixed minor typo in log output

