univention-management-console (3.0.80-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Stop logging the XML representation of input and output to /tmp/xmlin, since
    leaks information into /tmp depending on the umask and permits symlink attacks
    against data owned by www-data (Bug #21685)
  * Only log these files if debug level is 4 or higher

 -- Moritz Muehlenhoff <muehlenhoff@univention.de>  Thu, 03 Mar 2011 09:07:36 +0100

