univention-management-console (2.0.23-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * support UMCP status code 250: module asks for shutdown
  * Button: normally all values are verified before a command is
    issued. This can be deactivated now with the option verifiy_options =
    False
  * Button: with the new option icon_right = True the icon can be moved to
    the right side of the text
