    descriptions is possible; updated german translation

 -- Andreas BÃŒsching <buesching@univention.de>  Fri, 11 May 2007 16:22:44 +0200

univention-management-console (0.6.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * new button 'reset': set values of specified input fields back to default
  * enhanced support for layout options
  * support caching of startup requests
  * print a log message when loading of a module fails
  * support flag may_change in basic syntax classes
  * dynamic list: support predefined values
  * baseconfig module: more options for search, first step in supporting
    modification of existing variables and descriptions
  * fixes in module server: messages that are larger than the internal buffer
    of UNIX sockets can be processed now
  * set receive buffer to 16K in UMCP server and client
  * catch signal TERM to cleanup

 -- Andreas BÃŒsching <buesching@univention.de>  Fri, 11 May 2007 10:37:16 +0200

